## Core Dev Tools

### Claude Code
```bash
/usr/local/bin/claude

# Coding tasks
claude "implement X in Y"
claude --continue  # resume previous session

# With files
claude "review this" < myfile.py
```

### GitHub CLI
```bash
# Issues
gh issue list --repo infiquetra/<repo>
gh issue create --repo infiquetra/<repo> --title "..." --body "..."
gh issue edit <num> --add-assignee @me

# PRs
gh pr create --title "..." --body "..."
gh pr list --search "review-requested:@me"
gh pr review <num> --approve --body "LGTM"
gh pr merge <num> --squash

# Repos
gh repo list infiquetra
gh repo clone infiquetra/<repo>
```

### Git
```bash
git checkout -b {{ agent_name }}/<issue>-<description>
git add -p          # interactive staging
git commit -m "type(scope): description"
git push -u origin HEAD
```

