## Prometheus-Specific: Experiment Tracking

When evaluating new tech, document in `workspace/experiments/`:
```
workspace/experiments/
├── YYYY-MM-DD-<tool-name>.md   # experiment notes
└── results.md                  # outcomes summary
```

Template for experiment notes:
```markdown
# Experiment: <tool/approach>
Date: YYYY-MM-DD
Hypothesis: <what you expect>

## Setup
<how you tested it>

## Results
<what happened>

## Verdict
Adopt / Adopt with caveats / Reject
Reason: <why>
```
